ex.jsp?curl=pages/includes/medicines/medicines_landingpage.jsp&mid."[5] Pharmaceutical Society of Australia "APPGuide online. Australian prescription products guide online. Available from: URL: http://www.appco.com.au/appguide/default.asp." ([2006]):[6] Argov Z, Mastaglia FL "Drug-induced peripheral neuropathies." Br Med J 1 (1979): 663-6', 1767365204);
